== Filtered Models Plugin ==

- Introduction
- Installation 
- Use example
- Contact


Introduction
-------------------------

Rails 3 plugin which adds extra functionalities to the AtiveRecord class, allowing the developer
to use filter like methods that behave like the action filters for the Controllers.


Installation
-------------------------
In order to install this plugin, it should be enough to just copy the entire folder under vendor/plugins.



Use example
-------------------------

class Test < ActiveRecord::base
	before_filter :filter_method => [:filtered_method]
	after_filter :last_method => []

	def filter_method 
		# your filter code here
	end

	#Filtered methods must start with "__"
	def __filtered_method
		#  your code here
	end

	def last_method
		#this code will execute always after a method is invoked
	end
end


